amaze /əˈmeɪz/

(amazing,amazed,amazes) 

1. V-T/V-I If something amazes you, it surprises you very much. 使吃惊; 感到惊讶 

例： He amazed us by his knowledge of Colorado history. 他对于科罗拉多州历史的了解让我们吃惊。 

例： The 'Riverside' restaurant promises a variety of food that never ceases to amaze! “河畔”餐厅承诺提供永远给人惊奇的多种食品。 

2. amazed ADJ 吃惊的 

例： Most of the cast was amazed by the play's success. 演员班子中的大多数人对这出戏的成功感到吃惊。

</div>

